Package Shared

Class Submission

  • java.lang.Object
    • Shared.Submission
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Submission
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Provides data fields and methods to create a Java data-type, representing a Submission in a Learning Platform Java application. The overall purpose of this class is to store information to display and send between the client and server, and to used to store information about assignments that are submitted by students in courses.
    Since:
    March 5, 2018
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    A.Benaceur, M.Amouzai
